: \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1923}, {\"ngram\": \"any financial reward\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You dream of winning a gold medal - not money,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 2018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's the Olympics, the pinnacle for a track and field athlete, but you are putting a price on a gold.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"the pinnacle\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2051}, {\"ngram\": \"a track and field athlete\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"a price\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It certainly will not make Dina Asher-Smith for example run any quicker.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2149, \"end\": 2165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dina Asher-Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Lucrative endorsement and sponsorship deals for winning at the Olympics would dwarf the money on offer anyhow.\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2307, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lucrative endorsement\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2218}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsorship deals\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2240}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"the money\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2290}, {\"ngram\": \"offer\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am not sure how well this sits with the athletes from other events.\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"other events\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd be pretty annoyed and it really does not help relations.\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"relations\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is what they will be talking about in the camps.\\\"\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the camps\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold medal winners will only be eligible to take home \\u00a340k once they pass the anti-doping procedures, but Baulch recounted a conversation with now-Wales football head coach Craig Bellamy at the London Games that reinforced his position even further.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2672, \"end\": 2685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bellamy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.433879747561203e-24, \"text\": \"Craig Bellamy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bellamy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bellamy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gold medal winners\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00a340k\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"the anti-doping procedures\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"Baulch\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2611}, {\"ngram\": \"a conversation\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"the London Games\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2705}, {\"ngram\": \"his position\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [